data.title: M. Satchithanandan
data.meta_description: Murugan Satchithanandan is a Sri Lankan politician, former member of the Parliament of Sri Lanka and former government minister.
data.text:
Murugan Satchithanandan (Murugan Sachiththanantha) (born 22 August 1957) is a Sri Lankan politician,[1] former member of the Parliament of Sri Lanka and former government minister.
